Да будет ясен зрак окуляра,

~// +5 к {g|Encyclopedia:SpeedSpace}скорости{/g} торпед

May the ocular eye be forever clear,
May the enemies of the Omnissiah be cast down.
~// +5 torpedo {g|Encyclopedia:SpeedSpace}speed{/g}
